#t1一级range column二级key
#t2一级range column二级key
##实测分区数据分布为
#    p0sp0 p0sp1 p0sp2 p0sp3 p1sp0 p1sp1 p1sp2 p1sp3
#t2  3     2     4     0     3     8     4     1
